title: 'Boys and Girl - Offseason Storylines; Dez Bryant Talks Comeback, Cowboys, Dak, Motivation
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - Offseason Storylines; Dez Bryant Talks Comeback, Cowboys, Dak, Motivation
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby return to summarize some of the latest headlines surrounding America’s Team. Plus, former Cowboys wide receiver Dez Bryant sits down with Jane, Bobby, and his receivers coach David Robinson for an interview about his attempt to return to football. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
